(a) Build PASS on default + `--no-default-features --features "alloc parallel"`
(b) `cargo test -p cvvdp-cpu` PASS — all 45 tests stay green
(c) 1e-4 JOD parity floor PRESERVED — `standard_4k_path_still_at_parity_against_host_scalar`
