| Gate | Status | Notes |
|------|--------|-------|
| (a)  | PASS   | Builds on `std+parallel` (default), `alloc`, `alloc parallel`, `alloc parallel pixels` |
| (b)  | PASS   | 50 / 50 tests (45 original + 5 new SIMD parity tests) |
| (c)  | PASS   | JOD gate held at 1e-4 — no widening required |
| (d)  | PASS   | Clean clippy with module-level `manual_memcpy` allow (intentional per-tier SIMD pattern) |
| (e)  | PASS   | `cargo fmt --check` clean |
